{"tid":2119421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哇哇哇 琴日721香港開咗第一槍 咁少人知嘅","createTime":"2020-07-22T05:49:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T11:31:40.000Z","uid":259088,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9cb320ff7a6887c818856e4ad3e0d84b6a41d7b1","tid":2119421,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:49:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">賠償呀 NLM</span></span></strong><br />\n要賠償就大聲直接講出嚟啦 <br />\n香港都已經到咗<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">存亡</span></span></strong>關頭<br />\n依家明顯係<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">人禍</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9gGqoBY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9gGqoBY.jpg&h=c2089cf7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港短短幾日由個位確診數字爆升至<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">每日上百單</span></span></strong>，<br />\n仲未計算漏報遲報個案，同埋未病發隱形確診病人個案<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">力數政苦抗疫不力七宗罪</span></span></strong><br />\n（當然唔止七宗罪啦 大家自行加上去）<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">一 </span></strong> <strong>全方位容許豁免強制檢疫隱形病人喺全港散播病毒</strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">二 </span></strong>  <strong>不聽專家建議</strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">三 </span></strong>  <strong>牽累全港巿民生活苦不堪言</strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">四 </span></strong>  <strong>牽累全港各行各業瀕臨結業失業</strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">五 </span></strong>  <strong>牽累香港醫療系統崩潰 </strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">六 </span></strong>  <strong>牽累巿民健康生命受嚴重威脅家破人亡</strong><br />\n包括確診人士已過身，已感染病毒確診者同隱形病人等等等<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">七 </span></strong>  <strong>將香港變成巿民與病毒困獸鬥城巿</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">最近熱點：</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n爆料熱貼：<br />\n我係船員代理，有嘢想講<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2118934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2118934</a><br />\n<br />\n香港第三波疫情爆發 起因濃縮版熱貼：<br />\n嘩屌你老母,唔怪之得第三波爆到咁啦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2114196\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2114196</a><br />\n<br />\n最後 琴日<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">721</span></span></strong>連<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">竹君</span></span></strong>都加埋入嚟<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">爆料</span></span></strong>：<br />\n抗疫工作「<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">鬆弛</span></span></strong>有道」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n張竹君唔知佢邊處「鬆弛有道」呢？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2118521\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2118521</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n溫馨提示:<br />\n國安法下 令人對政府產生憎恨即屬違法,切勿以身試法千祈記得唔好<strong>share</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e3bab3fc0c3f164e7b5ced4e728beb4a53b18f","tid":2119421,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:54:48.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e6a20975e61037f9b612ad270487a13d81f262","tid":2119421,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T06:04:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54072951bfb35dedeb8a6f5e9bf9033dcafc64ef","tid":2119421,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi